title: Will United Natural Foods (UNFI) beat quarterly earnings?
description:
United Natural Foods is estimated to release earnings on September 30, 2025. The Street consensus estimate for United Natural Foods’s non-GAAP EPS for the relevant quarter is -$0.18.
